Attributes.description: Clinical practice to integrate and consolidate professional nursing knowledge, skills and competencies in the care of childbearing individuals, infants, and their families.
Attributes.prereq: Pre-reqs: All of NURS 300, NURS 310, NURS 321, NURS 322, NURS 330, NURS 352, NURS 360.
Attributes.coreq: Co-reqs: NURS 345 and one of NURS 323, NURS 401.
